# $FrauBSD: bdialog/NOTES 2020-05-11 11:19:01 -0700 freebsdfrau $

Major goals of bdialog (in order of importance):

1. Provide a BSD-licensed dialog utility for-use in FreeBSD base for the
   installer (bsdinstall) and configurator (bsdconfig)

2. Support terminal SIGWINCH (WINdow CHange SIGnal) event for live-resizing

3. LTR language support when supported by the terminal/console environment

4. Command-line compatibility with current /usr/bin/dialog

5. API compatiblity with dialog(3) C library

